{"tid":972707,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以為主人被困　英國吉娃娃勇衝火場送命","createTime":"2019-01-07T14:37:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T15:16:51.000Z","uid":32511,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"58b2c581b69a612dfec8b7df913acdc4d8bc3cdc","tid":972707,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:37:55.000Z","msg":"英國有一家人自駕露營車前往蘇格蘭（Scotland）打算旅行過新年，豈料途中露營車起火，爸爸救出一度被困的太太和女兒，一陣混亂後一家人及時逃出火海，但寵物犬吉娃娃以為主人仍然被困，獨自回到車上找主人，結果在爆炸中喪生。<br />\n <br />\n香港《蘋果日報》引述英國《每日鏡報》報導，來自肯特郡（Kent）的法蘭特和太太卡拉（Dan and Cara Farrant）與四名子女自駕前往蘇格蘭過新年，還帶上寵物犬吉娃娃「Coco」。但旅途中發生意外，上月29日，他們行駛到莫弗特（Moffatt）的公路時，露營車的引擎突然冒煙起火。<br />\n<br />\n法蘭特連忙拉3名兒子下車，但卡拉和女兒西婭（Thea）仍然被困車裡，當時乘客位置的車門卡住了，而火勢正不斷蔓延，險象環生；法蘭特抱起「Coco」，將牠從車窗拋出去，再營救太太和女兒。法蘭特回憶道︰「我永遠不會忘記那場面、不會忘記那些尖叫聲&hellip;&hellip;我記得一看過去，以為太遲了，卡拉和西婭被困在裡面、記得轉身發現火舌有我身後的整個擋風玻璃窗高。」<br />\n<br />\n幸好全部人都及時逃到安全的地方，但就在所有人放下心來的時候，忠心的「Coco」以為主人仍在車上，竟不顧危險，衝入火場找主人。法蘭特指︰「卡拉走去攔住路過的車子求救，發現『Coco』不在孩子身邊。」轉眼間還發生爆炸，「我們嘗試跑回去，但車子爆炸&hellip;&hellip;『Coco』在裡面。」消防員到場滅火後，在前座下方找到「Coco」的屍體。<br />\n<br />\n卡拉傷心地表示︰「『Coco』聽到我尖叫，我們想到，牠一定是回去救我和西婭。我希望『Coco』沒有回去救我。」養了「Coco」兩年，卡拉一家都為牠的離去而無比傷痛，孩子還會做噩夢想起當天的事，「『Coco』是凝聚一家人的力量，如果有人傷心或者病了，牠會陪伴在側。」法蘭特也表示︰「有幾秒我以為會失去太太和女兒，但原來，我們失去的是最好的友伴，我們的天使『Coco』。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k5Jn6fu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk5Jn6fu.png&h=87422134&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hwJSJ2b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhwJSJ2b.png&h=70b96b4a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yQn0SVw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyQn0SVw.png&h=a4f17703&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rx8rOtS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRx8rOtS.png&h=a38d8d06&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"946b42ee3e182ff181298081e74534dca16b813c","tid":972707,"uid":215603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:57:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0c0ef17f6617aced15fd2cbe8c6c6ce96cf0c92","tid":972707,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:57:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de01813da190a74c537ea8203c18b6078906ef35","tid":972707,"uid":117276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:58:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc2598a7950a3421ca545d04cf96141b8f554180","tid":972707,"uid":8951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:59:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa8af86e7eea0ad8639a98cda6c2d198709d147b","tid":972707,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:01:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c27bc3dc36f6022b09ce7c2994deb75abd76bc1e","tid":972707,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:01:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e25174bddf5ab586cc74613224f7650fcbf8eb6f","tid":972707,"uid":76753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:02:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10477fe48834ad8e6133ac2dfcb54ae521e54aad","tid":972707,"uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:03:22.000Z","msg":"吉娃娃<img src=\"/assets/faces/no